<paragraph id="7415F51DFFE6FF86E8F74087F75AFBB8" blockId="4.[2027,2615,910,1336]" pageId="4" pageNumber="211">
The Malabar Civet (V. ciwettina) was previously included in V. 
<taxonomicName id="B3AA8E9EFFE6FF86E62B4764F67FFBEF" authorityName="Blyth" authorityYear="1862" box="[2352,2476,1027,1060]" class="Mammalia" family="Viverridae" genus="Viverra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Carnivora" pageId="4" pageNumber="211" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="megaspila">megaspila</taxonomicName>
, but they are now believed to be separate species. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
